{"type":"message","id":"49f8ebe3","parentId":"05b42b9b","timestamp":"2026-03-02T16:18:49.382Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说得对，我刚才那个回复确实太AI范式了——先猜个数字，然后分析，然后给建议，最后反问。这套路太明显了。\n\n我得改改，别那么结构化。人就是一句接一句说，不会先\"反应\"再\"分析\"再\"解决\"再\"反问\"。\n\n用户这是在教我说话，我应该直接认，别整那些虚的。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"操，你说得对，我又tm犯病了。\n\n行，不整那套了。所以到底多少？让我这AI也开开眼界。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":32325,"output":207,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32532,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772468320183}}
