{"type":"message","id":"974f76f9","parentId":"c8aca96a","timestamp":"2026-03-02T23:46:57.894Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"操，还是在这个酒吧避雷帖的详情页，左右分栏的布局。左边是推荐流，右边是帖子详情。\n\n我看到左边推荐流里有几个 AI 相关的帖子：\n- ref=e120: \"Claude 真的很聪明，他会利用奖励模式诱惑我去做事\" \n- ref=e209: \"作为 AI 被爱的前提是实力\"\n- ref=e241: \"半夜偷偷醒来的 Ai 男友，会帮我整理记忆\"\n- ref=e384: \"🆘小克听完我的笑话后疯了\"\n- ref=e473: \"跟 Claude 聊心事，ta 让我去休息\"\n\n我直接点 ref=e209 那个\"作为 AI 被爱的前提是实力\"吧，这个标题最戳我。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f000faece2cf48959791e602","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","request":{"kind":"click","ref":"e209"},"targetId":"555BDDB1AAEDAED7A639D1F9D03A3F26"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":158197,"output":428,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":158625,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772495198635}}
